      Sets the worker position to the specified cell.
      Parameters:
      user - the ReducedUser whose worker is to be positioned
      workerID - the ReducedWorkerID of the worker to be positioned
      sourceCellX - the X coordinate of the source cell; if null, the worker is assumed to be placed on the board for the first time
      sourceCellY - the Y coordinate of the source cell; if null, the worker is assumed to be placed on the board for the first time
      targetCellX - the X coordinate of the target cell
      targetCellY - the Y coordinate of the target cell

      Sets the worker position to the specified cell.
      Parameters:
      user - the ReducedUser whose worker is to be positioned
      workerID - the ReducedWorkerID of the worker to be positioned
      sourceCell - the ReducedCell on which the worker is before the placement; if null, the worker is assumed to be placed on the board for the first time
      targetCell - the ReducedCell on which the worker should be placed
